{"id":"807852413579116544","type":"text","timestamp":1770428098,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/807852413579116544","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/sapphic-dice/807360609202110464\">sapphic-dice</a>:</p><blockquote><p>*grabs you by the face*</p><p>We are stronger than our worst impulses.</p><p>We are stronger than the pressure building. </p><p>Don’t be “normal”.</p><p>Be peculiar. </p><p>Be queer. </p><p>Be a freak. </p><p>*kisses your forehead*</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"sapphic-dice"},"post":{"id":"807360609202110464"}}],"baseline_notes":253,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}